        <p class="faded"><strong>(b) Updates and Troubleshooting</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;We may also use the collected information to contact you regarding updates or modifications to the Services or to help troubleshoot problems, provide you with required notices in connection with disputes between you and another user or alert you to changes in our policies or agreements that may affect your use of the Services.</p>

